Package: taxizedb
Type: Package
Title: Offline Access to Taxonomic Databases
Description: Download taxonomic databases, convert them into 'SQLite' format, 
    and query them locally for fast, reliable, and reproducible access to 
    taxonomic data.
Version: 0.3.2
